{"tid":756054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好sad好頹","createTime":"2018-07-25T16:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T12:44:59.000Z","uid":172705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51009dd570671d33c72fc31928fe2cdfbfcf3aab","tid":756054,"uid":172705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(利申我係絲)</span>成日諗起個前度根本冇愛過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊左年幾一係就出軌一係就無視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我俾曬我可以俾嘅嘢佢<br />\n但分手果下佢都冇乜感覺<br />\n我知一齊果陣唔係得我忍佢 佢都有忍我<br />\n自從我發現佢出軌就好小事都發脾氣<br />\n對佢亦故意冷淡左好多<br />\n我以為佢會因為我嘅冷淡更著緊我<br />\n點知佢就咁習慣左<br />\n冷淡對返我<br />\n其實咪又係逼緊我講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好攰但放唔低<br />\n覺得我付出左太多我唔捨得放手<br />\n但又明知佢對我冇愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家仲有聯絡不過都係打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以揾人屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a0d00949e315b42a87c871e237a778b8a8fe18","tid":756054,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"出軌都仲一齊 有咩好怨"},{"pid":"9fe8bbe07dc5a2b16a2ba43634ad9b5ee0316677","tid":756054,"uid":172705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a0d00949e315b42a87c871e237a778b8a8fe18","tid":756054,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"出軌都仲一齊 有咩好怨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"因為佢佔據左我生活嘅全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c8f3de99780fc8be1b507faed3a8398c81c7c5","tid":756054,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"421f6a73529c375c189d052f4cbe260bf3955505","tid":756054,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe8bbe07dc5a